      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle offering straightforward value for the next owner. This car shows its age but remains a compelling choice for someone seeking affordable transportation, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential. Priced to reflect its condition and deliver strong value, it\u2019s an honest opportunity at an accessible entry point.",
