    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option that could make a great runaround, first car, or little project for someone handy. A straightforward car at a sensible price, with a lot of value for anyone who wants cheap motoring without the big upfront cost. If you want something approachable, usable, and easy on the wallet, this is well worth a look.",
