      "description": "Budget-friendly car with good bones and plenty of usable life left for the right buyer. It shows its age cosmetically and will want some TLC, but the powertrain pulls through the rev range, starts up reliably, and the chassis still feels planted. A great option for a commuter, first car, or light project if you want something affordable with straightforward mechanical potential rather than overpaying for looks.",
