    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real presence\u2014an honest, road-worn machine that still turns heads with its unmistakable character. It has the kind of lived-in personality you can\u2019t fake, making it a great fit for someone who sees opportunity where others see age. Whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly runabout, a project with promise, or simply something with a story to tell, this one offers a compelling starting point and plenty of room to make it your own.",
