    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation or a practical project opportunity. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but for the buyer who wants straightforward value without a big upfront cost, it represents an honest, budget-conscious choice. A sensible option for commuting, light errands, or someone comfortable giving it the attention it may need.",
