    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a project to tinker with, or a handy extra vehicle to have around. It shows its age and has its share of wear, but it still has a lot to offer at a very approachable price. If you\u2019re after honest value and something you can drive, improve, and make your own, this is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
